data.description: MASSIVE 1 Acre lot with over 2,500 SQFT. This ELEGANT custom built CONTEMPORARY style home brings you tons of curb appeal, the homes exterior boasts BEAUTIFUL rock, stone, & brick. Through the front door you are greeted by a WELCOMING foyer and GORGEOUS ceramic tile. The formal dining room brings in an abundance of NATURAL LIGHT & features a MAJESTIC chandelier. The living room is SPACIOUS & OPEN to the FABULOUS kitchen that offers GRANITE counter-tops, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, double oven, BUILT-IN MICROWAVE, & a GLASS COOK-TOP. The main bedroom is opposite of the minor bedrooms & features BAY WINDOWS & LOVELY wood-looking CERAMIC TILE flooring. The main bathroom brings you in with its HUGE stand alone shower, GARDEN TUB, luxurious vanity, & His-and-Her closets. The backyard offers a spacious extended covered patio that is perfect for outside entrainment & family gatherings. Large shed and Playscape is included for your outdoor enjoyment. Come & see this SPECTACULAR home located inside of the EXPANDING subdivision of CACTUS CREEK
